--------------------------- RESUME GAME HERE -------------------------
Tarislar Garden Villa. The green bioluminescence of the Elven District 
filters through the glass. Alison is asleep in a real bed. Aris is 
drinking elven brandy, staring at the briefcase. You sit in the dark, 
head throbbing with a violet echo. You have 189k nuyen, but Silas 
Vane is dead. Tomorrow, you decide who you are.

What do you do?
